### Startup Command:

bin/dev (Do not use `rails s` directly, as it may cause js/css loading issues)

### The project uses the following tech stack:

Ruby on Rails 7.2
Tailwind CSS
Figaro
PostgreSQL
Simple_Form
High_Voltage
Active_Storage
Kaminari
Mina
Puma
RSpec

Do not add or remove any components and avoid upgrading or downgrading components lightly.

### Some important tips

Generate images using this placeholder website: https://images.unsplash.com/

Use `rails generate service xxx` to generate a service file
